fields.description: Indicates whether the user is deleted. Possible values are: true, false.
fields.name: IsDeleted

fields.description: Indicates whether a user's risky state is being processed by the backend.
fields.name: IsProcessing

fields.description: The date and time that the risky user was last updated.  The DateTimeOffset type represents date and time information using ISO 8601 format and is always in UTC time. For example, midnight UTC on Jan 1, 2014 is 2014-01-01T00:00:00Z.
fields.name: RiskLastUpdatedDateTime

fields.description: Level of the detected risky user. The possible values are low, medium, high, hidden, none, unknownFutureValue.
